Serverless API with Azure Functions


1) Create Resource Group
2) Create Azure Cosmos DB
3) Create Function App
4) Use the same Resource Group
5) Create new Storage Account with the Function App (Hosting)
6) Function API will be Serverless (Consumption)

7) Retrieve THe Primary Connection String from CosmosDB and Go to Function App
8) Go to Function App > Function > Create > HTTP Trigger (GET, POST, PUT) request

